{
  "taskId": "task_1778140614523_817",
  "requestedModel": "anti-gemini-3.1-pro-high",
  "text": "문서를 확인했습니다.\n요청하신 대로 버튼 정렬을 수정하고, 화려하고 현대적인 디자인으로 타이머를 전면 개편했습니다.\n\n애니메이션 그라데이션 배경과 네온 스타일의 타이머, 아이콘이 포함된 버튼으로 시각적 효과를 강화했습니다.\n\n```html\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"ko\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Futuristic Timer</title>\n    <link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com\">\n    <link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.gstatic.com\" crossorigin>\n    <link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@400;700&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <style>\n        @keyframes gradientAnimation {\n            0% { background-position: 0% 50%; }\n            50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }\n            100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Orbitron', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            height: 100vh;\n            margin: 0;\n            background: linear-gradient(-45deg, #0f0c29, #302b63, #24243e, #1a2a6c, #b21f1f, #fdbb2d);\n            background-size: 400% 400%;\n            animation: gradientAnimation 15s ease infinite;\n            color: #fff;\n        }\n\n        .timer-container {\n            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n            padding: 40px 50px;\n            border-radius: 20px;\n            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n            text-align: center;\n            width: 400px;\n            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);\n            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);\n            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);\n        }\n\n        #timerDisplay {\n            font-size: 4.5rem;\n            font-weight: 700;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            color: #fff;\n            letter-spacing: 4px;\n            text-shadow: \n                0 0 5px #00bfff,\n                0 0 10px #00bfff,\n                0 0 20px #00bfff,\n                0 0 40px #00bfff,\n                0 0 80px #00bfff;\n        }\n\n        .buttons {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: center;\n            gap: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .buttons button {\n            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;\n            font-size: 1rem;\n            font-weight: 400;\n            padding: 12px 20px;\n            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.5);\n            border-radius: 50px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: all 0.3s ease;\n            color: #00bfff;\n            background: transparent;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            gap: 8px;\n        }\n\n        .buttons button:hover {\n            background: rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.2);\n            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.5);\n            transform: translateY(-2px);\n        }\n        \n        .buttons button:active {\n            transform: translateY(0);\n        }\n\n        .buttons button svg {\n            width: 20px;\n            height: 20px;\n            fill: #00bfff;\n            transition: fill 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <div class=\"timer-container\">\n        <div id=\"timerDisplay\">00:00:00</div>\n        <div class=\"buttons\">\n            <button id=\"startButton\">\n                <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M8 5v14l11-7z\"></path></svg>\n                <span>Start</span>\n            </button>\n            <button id=\"pauseButton\">\n                <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M6 19h4V5H6v14zm8-14v14h4V5h-4z\"></path></svg>\n                <span>Pause</span>\n            </button>\n            <button id=\"resetButton\">\n                <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M17.65 6.35C16.2 4.9 14.21 4 12 4c-4.42 0-7.99 3.58-7.99 8s3.57 8 7.99 8c3.73 0 6.84-2.55 7.73-6h-2.08c-.82 2.33-3.04 4-5.65 4-3.31 0-6-2.69-6-6s2.69-6 6-6c1.66 0 3.14.69 4.22 1.78L13 11h7V4l-2.35 2.35z\"></path></svg>\n                <span>Reset</span>\n            </button>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <script>\n        let startTime;\n        let updatedTime;\n        let difference;\n        let tInterval;\n        let savedTime = 0;\n        let paused = true;\n        let running = false;\n\n        const timerDisplay = document.getElementById('timerDisplay');\n        const startButton = document.getElementById('startButton');\n        const pauseButton = document.getElementById('pauseButton');\n        const resetButton = document.getElementById('resetButton');\n\n        function startTimer() {\n            if (!running) {\n                startTime = new Date().getTime();\n                if (savedTime) {\n                    startTime -= savedTime;\n                }\n                tInterval = setInterval(getShowTime, 1);\n                paused = false;\n                running = true;\n            }\n        }\n\n        function pauseTimer() {\n            if (running) {\n                clearInterval(tInterval);\n                savedTime = new Date().getTime() - startTime;\n                paused = true;\n                running = false;\n            }\n        }\n\n        function resetTimer() {\n            clearInterval(tInterval);\n            savedTime = 0;\n            difference = 0;\n            paused = true;\n            running = false;\n            timerDisplay.innerHTML = '00:00:00';\n        }\n\n        function getShowTime() {\n            updatedTime = new Date().getTime();\n            difference = updatedTime - startTime;\n\n            let hours = Math.floor((difference % (1000 * 60 * 60 * 24)) / (1000 * 60 * 60));\n            let minutes = Math.floor((difference % (1000 * 60 * 60)) / (1000 * 60));\n            let seconds = Math.floor((difference % (1000 * 60)) / 1000);\n\n            hours = (hours < 10) ? \"0\" + hours : hours;\n            minutes = (minutes < 10) ? \"0\" + minutes : minutes;\n            seconds = (seconds < 10) ? \"0\" + seconds : seconds;\n\n            timerDisplay.innerHTML = hours + ':' + minutes + ':' + seconds;\n        }\n        \n        // PAUSE/RESUME LOGIC FIX: Pause button should be a toggle\n        // The original logic was flawed. Let's simplify.\n        // Start button starts or resumes. Pause button pauses. Reset button resets.\n        // Let's refine the logic to be more intuitive.\n        // What if Start becomes Pause and vice versa? That's more common.\n        // But the user has 3 buttons. Let's keep them separate but make the logic robust.\n\n        // Corrected logic:\n        // Start: only works if not running.\n        // Pause: only works if running.\n        // Reset: works anytime.\n        \n        // Let's stick to the user's explicit buttons and fix the JS logic slightly for robustness.\n        // The original JS had a bug where resuming from pause would reset the savedTime.\n        // My new logic above fixes that.\n        \n        startButton.addEventListener('click', startTimer);\n        pauseButton.addEventListener('click', pauseTimer);\n        resetButton.addEventListener('click', resetTimer);\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n```\n\n<file_operations>\n[\n  {\n    \"action\": \"write\",\n    \"type\": \"output\",\n    \"path\": \"index.html\",\n    \"content\": \"<!DOCTYPE html>\\n<html lang=\\\"ko\\\">\\n<head>\\n    <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\">\\n    <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\">\\n    <title>Futuristic Timer</title>\\n    <link rel=\\\"preconnect\\\" href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com\\\">\\n    <link rel=\\\"preconnect\\\" href=\\\"https://fonts.gstatic.com\\\" crossorigin>\\n    <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@400;700&display=swap\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\">\\n    <style>\\n        @keyframes gradientAnimation {\\n            0% { background-position: 0% 50%; }\\n            50% { background-position: 100% 50%; }\\n            100% { background-position: 0% 50%; }\\n        }\\n\\n        body {\\n            font-family: 'Orbitron', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;\\n            display: flex;\\n            justify-content: center;\\n            align-items: center;\\n            height: 100vh;\\n            margin: 0;\\n            background: linear-gradient(-45deg, #0f0c29, #302b63, #24243e, #1a2a6c, #b21f1f, #fdbb2d);\\n            background-size: 400% 400%;\\n            animation: gradientAnimation 15s ease infinite;\\n            color: #fff;\\n        }\\n\\n        .timer-container {\\n            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\\n            padding: 40px 50px;\\n            border-radius: 20px;\\n            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\\n            text-align: center;\\n            width: 400px;\\n            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);\\n            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);\\n            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);\\n        }\\n\\n        #timerDisplay {\\n            font-size: 4.5rem;\\n            font-weight: 700;\\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\\n            color: #fff;\\n            letter-spacing: 4px;\\n            text-shadow: \\n                0 0 5px #00bfff,\\n                0 0 10px #00bfff,\\n                0 0 20px #00bfff,\\n                0 0 40px #00bfff,\\n                0 0 80px #00bfff;\\n        }\\n\\n        .buttons {\\n            display: flex;\\n            justify-content: center;\\n            gap: 20px;\\n        }\\n\\n        .buttons button {\\n            font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;\\n            font-size: 1rem;\\n            font-weight: 400;\\n            padding: 12px 20px;\\n            border: 1px solid rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.5);\\n            border-radius: 50px;\\n            cursor: pointer;\\n            transition: all 0.3s ease;\\n            color: #00bfff;\\n            background: transparent;\\n            display: flex;\\n            align-items: center;\\n            justify-content: center;\\n            gap: 8px;\\n        }\\n\\n        .buttons button:hover {\\n            background: rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.2);\\n            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 191, 255, 0.5);\\n            transform: translateY(-2px);\\n        }\\n        \\n        .buttons button:active {\\n            transform: translateY(0);\\n        }\\n\\n        .buttons button svg {\\n            width: 20px;\\n            height: 20px;\\n            fill: #00bfff;\\n            transition: fill 0.3s ease;\\n        }\\n\\n    </style>\\n</head>\\n<body>\\n\\n    <div class=\\\"timer-container\\\">\\n        <div id=\\\"timerDisplay\\\">00:00:00</div>\\n        <div class=\\\"buttons\\\">\\n            <button id=\\\"startButton\\\">\\n                <svg xmlns=\\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\\" width=\\\"24\\\" height=\\\"24\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\"><path d=\\\"M8 5v14l11-7z\\\"></path></svg>\\n                <span>Start</span>\\n            </button>\\n            <button id=\\\"pauseButton\\\">\\n                <svg xmlns=\\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\\" width=\\\"24\\\" height=\\\"24\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\"><path d=\\\"M6 19h4V5H6v14zm8-14v14h4V5h-4z\\\"></path></svg>\\n                <span>Pause</span>\\n            </button>\\n            <button id=\\\"resetButton\\\">\\n                <svg xmlns=\\\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\\" width=\\\"24\\\" height=\\\"24\\\" viewBox=\\\"0 0 24 24\\\"><path d=\\\"M17.65 6.35C16.2 4.9 14.21 4 12 4c-4.42 0-7.99 3.58-7.99 8s3.57 8 7.99 8c3.73 0 6.84-2.55 7.73-6h-2.08c-.82 2.33-3.04 4-5.65 4-3.31 0-6-2.69-6-6s2.69-6 6-6c1.66 0 3.14.69 4.22 1.78L13 11h7V4l-2.35 2.35z\\\"></path></svg>\\n                <span>Reset</span>\\n            </button>\\n        </div>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <script>\\n        let startTime;\\n        let updatedTime;\\n        let difference;\\n        let tInterval;\\n        let savedTime = 0;\\n        let paused = true;\\n        let running = false;\\n\\n        const timerDisplay = document.getElementById('timerDisplay');\\n        const startButton = document.getElementById('startButton');\\n        const pauseButton = document.getElementById('pauseButton');\\n        const resetButton = document.getElementById('resetButton');\\n\\n        function startTimer() {\\n            if (!running) {\\n                startTime = new Date().getTime();\\n                if (savedTime) {\\n                    startTime -= savedTime;\\n                }\\n                tInterval = setInterval(getShowTime, 1);\\n                paused = false;\\n                running = true;\\n            }\\n        }\\n\\n        function pauseTimer() {\\n            if (running) {\\n                clearInterval(tInterval);\\n                savedTime = new Date().getTime() - startTime;\\n                paused = true;\\n                running = false;\\n            }\\n        }\\n\\n        function resetTimer() {\\n            clearInterval(tInterval);\\n            savedTime = 0;\\n            difference = 0;\\n            paused = true;\\n            running = false;\\n            timerDisplay.innerHTML = '00:00:00';\\n        }\\n\\n        function getShowTime() {\\n            updatedTime = new Date().getTime();\\n            difference = updatedTime - startTime;\\n\\n            let hours = Math.floor((difference % (1000 * 60 * 60 * 24)) / (1000 * 60 * 60));\\n            let minutes = Math.floor((difference % (1000 * 60 * 60)) / (1000 * 60));\\n            let seconds = Math.floor((difference % (1000 * 60)) / 1000);\\n\\n            hours = (hours < 10) ? \\\"0\\\" + hours : hours;\\n            minutes = (minutes < 10) ? \\\"0\\\" + minutes : minutes;\\n            seconds = (seconds < 10) ? \\\"0\\\" + seconds : seconds;\\n\\n            timerDisplay.innerHTML = hours + ':' + minutes + ':' + seconds;\\n        }\\n        \\n        startButton.addEventListener('click', startTimer);\\n        pauseButton.addEventListener('click', pauseTimer);\\n        resetButton.addEventListener('click', resetTimer);\\n    </script>\\n\\n</body>\\n</html>\"\n  }\n]\n</file_operations>\n<review_request>\n{\n  \"title\": \"[리뷰] 타이머 UI/UX 개선\",\n  \"assignee\": \"dev_advisor\",\n  \"message\": \"사용자 피드백에 따라 타이머 디자인을 전면 개편했습니다. 버튼 정렬 문제를 해결하고, 애니메이션 그라데이션 및 네온 효과를 적용하여 시각적으로 화려하게 수정했습니다. 코드 리뷰 부탁드립니다.\"\n}\n</review_request>",
